udicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PTDM/110%2c%e8%a8%b4%2c139%2c20220225%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PTDM,110,訴,139,20220225,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"139","JDATE":"20220225","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}